.SH "NAME"
\fBslim\-describe\fR \- describe an app and its dependencies
.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
\fBslim\fR \fBdescribe\fR [(\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR_)] [(\fB\-r\fR|\fB\-\-repository=\fR)<repository>] [(\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output=\fR)<filename>] <app\-source>
