.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Describes a Splunk app and its dependencies, assuming the \fBapp\.manifest\fR file is located at the root of the app source directory\.
.
.SH "OPTIONS"
<app\-source> Location of the app source package or directory\.
.
.P
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
